<!-- COLONNE 3 : PLANCHE -->
<section class="panel panel--sheet" aria-label="Planche d'impression">
  <div class="panel__header">
    <h2 class="panel__title">3. Planche A4 (<span id="sheetCount">0</span>/<span id="sheetMax">6</span>)</h2>
    <div class="panel__tools">
      <button id="btnPrint" type="button" class="btn btn--yellow" disabled>
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 6 2 18 2 18 9"/><path d="M6 18H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v5a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2"/><rect x="6" y="14" width="12" height="8"/></svg>
        Imprimer
      </button>
      <button id="btnClear" type="button" class="btn btn--ghost btn--sm" disabled>
        Vider
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="sheet-thumb" aria-label="Apercu reduit de la planche">
    <div id="sheetGrid" class="sheet-grid">
      <!-- Etiquettes ajoutees ici en JS -->
    </div>
    <div id="sheetEmpty" class="sheet-empty">
      <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/><line x1="9" y1="3" x2="9" y2="21"/></svg>
      <p>Planche vide.<br>Remplis le formulaire et clique sur <strong>Ajouter</strong>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="panel__hint">
    Apres impression, decoupe a la cisaille en suivant les lignes pointillees.
  </p>
  <p class="panel__hint panel__hint--tip">
    <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"/></svg>
    <span>Pour un rendu 1:1 a la bonne taille, choisis <strong>Marges : Aucunes</strong> et <strong>Echelle : 100&nbsp;%</strong> dans le dialogue d'impression.</span>
  </p>
</section>
